<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login Successful</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #777;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #4CAF50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .cta-button {
        padding: 12px 24px;
      }
      .email-container {
        padding: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Welcome Back, <%= @user.username %>!</h1>

    <h2>You have logged in successfully.</h2>

    <p>We are thrilled to have you back. You can now access your dashboard, manage your account, and enjoy all the features available to you.</p>

    <p>If you didn't log in, please <a href="[Your Support URL]">contact support</a> immediately to secure your account.</p>

    <a href="[Your Dashboard URL]" class="cta-button">Go to Your Dashboard</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you need any help, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing [Your Platform Name]!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
